@node Installation
@chapter Installation
@cindex installation
@cindex setup
@cindex Ubuntu

This chapter walks through a complete install of the OwnSona MCP server
on a fresh Ubuntu 24.04 LTS system.  It is the canonical
``build-from-scratch'' procedure; if you have a recent backup,
@ref{Restore from backup} at the end of the chapter is faster.

Everything assumes you can @code{sudo}.  Commands shown without
@code{sudo} should run as the @code{ownsona} user (created in
@ref{Create the ownsona user}).

